DOC.brief_summary: We proposed to compare outcomes in women with DOR undergoing ART with rec-FSH + u-HMH with those with u-FSH only in GnRH antagonist protocols.
DOC.brief_title: Efficacy of Urinary Follicle-Stimulating Hormone (FSH) Among Poor Responders
DOC.criteria: At least one trial with adequate ovarian stimulation resulted by 4 or less oocytes retrieval. High responder patients
